summary:
- Programme Advisor for the Climate and Energy Response Facility of The Netherlands Enterprise Agency (RVO). 
- Geologist specialised in geothermal energy development. 
- Connector with the themes renewables, energy transition, (ground)water, geo-engineering, soil and - agriculture.
